cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.CE 

This paper discusses AI Planning and its application in automated Web Service Composition. Therefore, cs.AI is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the reasoning required for belief update, which is related to machine learning and could fall under cs.LG. The paper also mentions the use of planning tools, which could fall under cs.PL. The paper also discusses the computational properties of the forward effects case, which could fall under cs.CE. Finally, the paper discusses the application of planning under uncertainty, which could fall under cs.SE.
